Description:
   Solar Invocation is a Cleric prayer ritual that invokes Disk's solar
   aspect, calling for divine blessing and empowerment through sustained
   devotion. The Cleric enters a brief meditative invocation, and if their
   faith is sufficient, Disk responds with a blessing that improves the
   Cleric's overall combat and healing effectiveness.

   Solar Invocation is the Cleric's primary self-buff prayer. The effect
   enhances the potency of subsequent healing spells and slightly improves
   the Cleric's divine combat capabilities. It represents the Cleric
   entering a heightened state of divine alignment, where Disk's will flows
   more freely through them. The invocation must be performed at rest
   (standing position) as it requires focused devotional attention.
*******************************************************************************
